So of the original 40 champs this game had, only 14 have Legendary level skins:
{{champion:31}} {{champion:40}} {{champion:10}} {{champion:75}} {{champion:17}} {{champion:18}} {{champion:23}} {{champion:45}} {{champion:34}} {{champion:22}} {{champion:36}} {{champion:11}} {{champion:20}} {{champion:14}} 

Of the remaining 26, 13 will probably need a rework before they can get one:
{{champion:32}} {{champion:9}} {{champion:54}} {{champion:25}} {{champion:33}} {{champion:13}} {{champion:26}} {{champion:53}} {{champion:42}} {{champion:24}} {{champion:38}} {{champion:35}} {{champion:16}} 

This leaves us with 13 poor unfortunate souls in need of a good Legendary skin, and some of them are really damn popular.
Now, some do have &#039;Legendary+ skins&#039;, but I&#039;m not 100% they count as such:
{{champion:12}} {{champion:1}} {{champion:74}} {{champion:4}} 
Leaving us with:
{{champion:28}} {{champion:15}} {{champion:19}} {{champion:41}}  {{champion:30}} {{champion:55}} {{champion:27}} {{champion:44}} {{champion:29}} 

Who do you think should get one?
My personal favorites would be {{champion:55}} for a Legendary one, and {{champion:41}} for an Ultimate one, considering they skipped Top lane last time.
